OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FDry with
OL,6,Fsome late sunshine this evening.
OL,7,FStaying dry for the rest of the night
OL,8,Fbut clouding over from the east. Most
OL,9,Fof the west coast remaining clear.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FRather cloudy at first in
OL,12,Fthe Central Belt, but all staying dry
OL,13,Fand turning increasingly sunny from
OL,14,Flate morning. Best of sunshine across
OL,15,Fthe west where it will feel warm.
OL,16,
OL,17,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,18,Fand settled with plenty of sunshine,
OL,19,Fovernight low cloud in the east soon
OL,20,Fburning off. Feeling warm in the
OL,21,Fsunshine.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
